{"tid":510941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"父母不愛、沒朋友　國中少女到處找男性交","createTime":"2017-12-27T03:41:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T15:18:51.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"61a9a8c3beb591fee3144cf801e61bb50583b9ba","tid":510941,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T03:41:12.000Z","msg":"《聯合報》報導，新北市一名15歲國中少女，因自覺得父母不關心、朋友不愛她，竟上網到處找男網友發生性關係，藉此獲得肯定以及歸屬感，許多男網友見到有年輕女孩投懷送抱，均同意見面發生性關係。<br />\n<br />\n社工發現少女行為後趕緊通知檢警，不過少女不願對這些男網友提告，檢警依據她跟網友們的聊天紀錄，陸續傳喚10多名男網友，依妨害性自主罪嫌偵辦。<br />\n其中一位26歲詹姓男子坦承今年6月有透過LINE約這名少女見面，並要求「幫他口交」，少女也欣然同意，詹男承認犯行，也透露少女說過自己未滿16歲，檢方認定犯行明確，今依與未成年女子性交罪提起公訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20171227/1266983\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20171227%2F1266983&d=9XDN3Mps%2F8vLzcjwtXctS%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=b2ceec4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20171227%2F1266983&h=e224734d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20171227/1266983</a><br />\n<br />\n連登有愛"},{"pid":"abc1319ec06f00ae3c0e88f486186f39a9940ae9","tid":510941,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T03:47:50.000Z","msg":"新北市分數已達上限"},{"pid":"9a2633693afc6580da6e25d338e9aa0714d1b963","tid":510941,"uid":65774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T03:52:03.000Z","msg":"落仔萍 Bren lui?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8659a45afa25ca4d32f1c6f49d56dc03c8e7a2df","tid":510941,"uid":11962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T03:54:30.000Z","msg":"寶島<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"884d02def7c99ba1d0024dde101b52f98d19d482","tid":510941,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20